### Test API Endpoints
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or copy to Postman

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@prodUrl = https://your-project-name.vercel.app

### ============================================
### LOCAL TESTING
### ============================================

### 1. Health Check (Local)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Root Endpoint (Local)
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 3. Decode Simple Text (Local)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/brute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ciphertext": "Khoor Zruog",
  "language": "auto"
}

### 4. Decode Long Text (Local)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/brute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ciphertext": "Wklv lv d whvw phvvdjh iru fubswdqdobvlv",
  "language": "auto"
}

### 5. Decode Kinyarwanda (Local)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/brute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ciphertext": "Ltrzmyd",
  "language": "auto"
}

### ============================================
### PRODUCTION TESTING (After Vercel Deploy)
### ============================================

### 6. Health Check (Production)
GET {{prodUrl}}/health

### 7. Decode Simple Text (Production)
POST {{prodUrl}}/api/brute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ciphertext": "Khoor Zruog",
  "language": "auto"
}

### 8. Decode Long Text (Production)
POST {{prodUrl}}/api/brute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ciphertext": "Wklv lv d whvw phvvdjh iru fubswdqdobvlv",
  "language": "auto"
}
